    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317510/extras/491718fe8a1d9f3891c19feb4e91591f.apng?t=1745217922\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317510/extras/491718fe8a1d9f3891c19feb4e91591f.poster.avif?t=1745217922\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=120 /></picture></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to SokobotS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SokobotS is a cooperative sokoban game with goofy robots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover Sokobots:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>solo</strong> or in <strong>coop</strong> with different robots!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resolve <strong>sokoban puzzles</strong> with many interactions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control different robots with many <strong>abilities</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interact</strong> with <strong>other  rooms</strong> to help each others!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the plan of the evil Chococorp compagny...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a (very) unique story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the future, all industries are controled by a <strong>chocolate cereal lobby</strong> called Chococorp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When scientist discover that an asteroid belt with <strong>the most sugary chocolate ever</strong> is close to earth, Chococorp send robots to extract as many chocolate as possible. No matter what it cost...</p>",
